    "description": "Give healthy eating a kick with sticky jerk-spiced pork. You'll coat juicy pork steak in jerk paste before pan frying till charred. Serve up with sweet potato mash, creamy slaw and more jerk sauce to finish. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
